**Differentiation:** Every competitor tells readers *what* the differences are — Mirellé should tell them *which choice is theirs* with a genuine decision framework. We build a "find your shape" lens that maps hand type + lifestyle + nail art preference to a confident recommendation. No competitor does all three together. We also go deeper on the emotional dimension: these readers are at the salon or checkout screen right now and feeling confused — we speak to that anxiety directly.

